# Critical Escalation Runbook

## Immediate Response (< 15 min)

1. Isolate affected systems
2. Page security lead and on-call engineer simultaneously
3. Open P0 incident ticket
4. Notify legal and compliance team

## Escalation Matrix

| Severity | Response Time | Escalation Path |
|----------|--------------|-----------------|
| P0 (Critical) | 15 min | On-call → Security Lead → CTO |
| P1 (High) | 1 hour | On-call → Security Lead |
| P2 (Medium) | 4 hours | On-call engineer |

## Communication

- Internal: incident channel immediately
- External: PR team approves all statements — no individual communication
- Regulatory: legal team handles within required timeframe
